params.newOwner: The new owner of the contract.

OwnershipTransferred(address,address).notice: Emitted when ownership is moved from one address to another.

owner().notice: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().notice: Leaves the contract without owner. Can only be called by the current owner. This is a dangerous call be aware of the consequences

transferOwnership(address).notice: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new address. Emits an [`OwnershipTransferred`](#ownershiptransferred) event indicating the transfered ownership. Requirements: - Can only be called by the current owner.
